-- Switchblade --

Switchblade watches the odd bot's procession on the holo=map. He 
still had work to do, and he didn't want to leave this bot to wander 
around the base.

He opens a base comm to Pheonix, "Hey... get back to the control 
room. I have to work to do, and I don't want to be held up by the 
likes of you."
